snippet.title: Ragdoll Runners - Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ragdoll Runners is available on Steam!
- Try the web demo here: https://sman.itch.io/ragdoll-runners
- Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/404820

Ragdoll Runners is a physics-based track & field game where you control independently the two legs of an athlete to compete in 8 events of 4 types: sprint, long jump, triple jump and hurdles.

For those who claim I copied QWOP, please read that: http://ragdollrunners.com/ragdoll-runners-development-history/
(TL;DR: I published a version of Ragdoll Runners two years before the release of QWOP)

- Website: http://ragdollrunners.com
- Twitter: http://twitter.com/RagdollRunners
- Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ragdollrunners

Musics:
“Lord, Have Mercy (Gospodi, pomiluj)”
by Dr. Emiliyan Stankov
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

"The Haunted Hotel" 
by SackJo22
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

“HeavyVirus - Memories”
http://youtube.com/mmmontagemusic
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
